,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />月尾再提"},{"pid":"51ce3c5047edfd749dc900638bc6ee92bbe829c9","tid":1613540,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57782b226aa23966871a4b44cd22d7e2bfadbfd3","tid":1613540,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:24:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d02e66c1db2beadb96c70127947a2da45dcf120d","tid":1613540,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T20:52:39.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"01805173f0f1512e97a314111db711cac43eaa1f","tid":1613540,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adf9310c4bb52f8397fc1b33afe2039027281ba","tid":1613540,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1b6c91ecc694cd0b9021e087e475380367bc03f","tid":1613540,"uid":289649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"7c72f1210594a95c8d06acc7b769721983202c49","tid":1613540,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"09dfbd32040f01f6a08def4b5d94487f7fdef3b0","tid":1613540,"uid":285118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"大家差不多時間啦"},{"pid":"db64644a572b6fb83ec24177b904236a1fea6c10","tid":1613540,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522e0ace51a6089c69319111a58b503890723f61","tid":1613540,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:54:03.000Z","msg":"繼續換美金"},{"pid":"de079e9f14df098fdbd8f9a2872c56def3a93f03","tid":1613540,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:54:08.000Z","msg":"撳USD <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 藍罷買，黃幫襯"},{"pid":"0d23b25a708aaca692de2bb26c33654672af7922","tid":1613540,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de079e9f14df098fdbd8f9a2872c56def3a93f03","tid":1613540,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:54:08.000Z","msg":"撳USD <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 藍罷買，黃幫襯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f